rComments: People were really hard on her, but she was one of my favourite profs. She explains things again if students seem confused, and she tries her best to make sure everyone is up to speed. She is VERY patient, especially with those who talk in class and come late. Her expectations are reasonable and clear. Very nice prof, available to help when needed.

Every powerpoint is on Virtual Campus and we do exercices in class so she can help us. Don't expect linguistic teaching. We learn Spanish, without the learning the origins and other stuff you might want in a foreign language class.
